{"tid":1626854,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"伊拉克10月1開始爆發全國性示威 已死93人 傷1600多人","createTime":"2019-10-05T13:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:37:06.000Z","uid":44751,"like":112,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c1dcd9e25a477f6beb49e3925c002d45032faeab","tid":1626854,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:20:32.000Z","msg":"「把我們殺光，或者我們把政府換掉」 <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n伊拉克10月1日爆發全國性反政府示威，成千上萬年輕人自發性走上街頭，鎮暴警察頻與未武裝的民眾發生血腥衝突，使用水砲、催淚瓦斯、橡膠子彈甚至實彈來對付百姓。<br />\n<br />\n伊拉克政府宵禁、斷網、實彈鎮壓。<br />\n目前至少93人喪生，1600人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n香港、印尼、伊拉克<br />\n<br />\n民主得來不易，台灣人千萬守住。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/114716416598333/posts/119713679431940?sfns=mo//\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F114716416598333%2Fposts%2F119713679431940%3Fsfns%3Dmo%2F%2F&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=ca25c4d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/114716416598333/posts/119713679431940?sfns=mo//</a><br />\n<br />\n全世界陷入示威潮 唔知香港係咪其中一個因素<br />\n雖然印尼同伊克克同香港嘅環境同人差太遠<br />\n不過香港人都可以借鑑一下人地嘅示威嘅水平<br />\n唔係批評啲咩 但香港暫時仲未配得上什麼獨立<br />\n包括我自己係一舊垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家加油 我深信香港不會輸的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1085f95b999f85b229d3568c9df91247997a4000","tid":1626854,"uid":103230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:22:32.000Z","msg":"伊拉克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24734e2026146916f508cd760b1274f53312cc0b","tid":1626854,"uid":44751,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QpRPA38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpRPA38.jpg&h=cd5c2341&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c08a2036dfa46019f18003f8bed18c1800eb95e4","tid":1626854,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:23:43.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"9743c1191affbd813682e061303db8940dd04bdf","tid":1626854,"uid":28831,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"全世界反極權邁向民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e61a818330f8f3e43d5bd61d1534f92cab63be","tid":1626854,"uid":46966,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係反共產黨"},{"pid":"a30c84e4fd336d167f93b87c3b57e7fc9bcfefb0","tid":1626854,"uid":187510,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"香港燃起革命之火"},{"pid":"8b12f7b87bd9e7ae9158dbb5c3922f1c64345cd1","tid":1626854,"uid":53003,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"藍絲一定拍到手掌都爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就話香港警察好溫和<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d399e797960adf05cb505c76de12199d3b966da1","tid":1626854,"uid":125727,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:26:49.000Z","msg":"佢地實彈 竟然冇叛軍肯企出嚟  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75afd7c1d1586eeace1fb81d95a05d37777f55c5","tid":1626854,"uid":137493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"真槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40f448591d02aac798d4f4a457db240bd1c6069","tid":1626854,"uid":302917,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"8b12f7b87bd9e7ae9158dbb5c3922f1c64345cd1","tid":1626854,"uid":53003,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"藍絲一定拍到手掌都爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就話香港警察好溫和<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" 